Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《末世》前情回顧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Revolution...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從來沒讓我按照自己的意愿做過事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have never once let me do things my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想得到一個機會  我給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want a shot, you got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody, run, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芥子氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's mustard gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天失去了二十個手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We lost 20 men today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁爾斯  唯一重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only thing that matters, Miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是打敗這些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is beating these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁爾斯  怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miles, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將堿液和水混合  就能中和芥氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mix lye and water, and it neutralizes mustard gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在沒辦法和他們對抗了  邁爾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we got nothing to fight 'em with, Miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗恩  這是芥氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marion, this is mustard gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛國者對我們使用這東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Patriots are using this stuff on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能比你更能盯著圖魯門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody has better eyes on Truman than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我們他想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us what he's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是納米機器人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the nano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我們說的做  會把普里西拉還給你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just do what we say, and you will get Priscilla back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時  你要做我們的指導\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, you will be our guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你不能告訴任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要邁爾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't need Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要殺死我  湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to kill me, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就殺死我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開這孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna let the boy go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有活兒要忙呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and me-- we've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么活兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉婭死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Julia's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛國者們殺了她  因為我沒法抓住你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The patriots killed her because I couldn't catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們本來也不會放了她的  湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were never gonna let her go, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰森也是這么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what Jason said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一次一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am gonna take the patriots down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉愛國者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one corpse at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走小道去華盛頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am gonna cut a path to Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著總統的頭開一槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and put a bullet in the President's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓謝爾曼將軍的遠征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make Sherman's March
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是十公里長跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}feel like a 10k fun run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這種事感興趣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that the sort of work that you'd be interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和我的胃口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is music to my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那邁爾斯呢  -邁爾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What about Miles? - Miles...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得邁爾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You--you think Miles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不同意那樣做嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不愿意放手一搏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not willing to do what it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十點半前裝滿兩個水柜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have both tanks filled by 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清潔儀表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clean the gauges.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,232號出去打水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}2-3-2 going out for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喬嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定沒人看見你們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure no one saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們懂行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許瑪麗恩說你們沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe Marion says you're okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不認識你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是  哥們  臂章不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same here, buddy. Nice armband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么知道你不會告發我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do we know you're not gonna turn us in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-也許我該這樣做  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, maybe I should. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗恩說你沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marion says you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗恩說我們沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marion says we're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見芥氣了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you seen the mustard gas or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少桶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many barrels we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一桶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桶  你說就一桶是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One? What do you mean, one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看朝著基地那個車廂的尾部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look close at the end of the car toward the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃十字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yellow cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們給芥氣的符號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their little code for mustard gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一罐車都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whole damn tanker car full of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是個問題  -你覺得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's a problem. - You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道誰能在這件事上幫忙嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know who would've been helpful with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門羅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在可能已經往北走了一半路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, he's probably halfway north by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說  不幸的是  我們只能靠你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which means, sadly, we're left with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}銘記烈士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣  喜好不會變\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same as always. The man likes what he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很忙  布萊恩  你去忙你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you're busy, Brian. You go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我來布置  -是  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let me set up. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我最喜歡的  -來吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My favorite. - Come on and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你沒找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it you didn't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了24小時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都沒看到亞倫和普里西拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no sign of Aaron or Priscilla anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得找他們  所有人都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to look for them, all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  這是個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it. It's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是我們唯一的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's not our only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定照片里是卡弗將軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sure it was General Carver in that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是德州總統  我知道他的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's the President of Texas. I know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的照片  還有黃十字標志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was his picture and that yellow cross symbol,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃  日程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}plans, schedules,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有圈出的日期  就是明天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a circled date, tomorrow's date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切真是太糟糕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that all adds up to awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他們要把毒氣運往奧斯汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think they're sending the gas to Austin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛國者們以前試圖謀殺過卡弗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Patriots tried to kill Carver once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他們只是加倍加注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now they're just doubling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往首都投毒氣  殺死幾千人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gas the capitol. Kill a couple thousand people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栽贓給加州  打造珍珠港事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pin it on California. Stage their own Pearl Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那沒法阻止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then there's no stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德州和加州宣戰  消滅對方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Texas and California go to war, wipe each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛國者們接管剩下的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Patriots take over the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能中和毒氣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can we neutralize the gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒法偷運那么多堿液\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never sneak that much lye into the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也許...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  你得獨自去找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel, you're gonna have to find Aaron
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞倫和普里西拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Priscilla alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -那你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sorry. - What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要偷一輛火車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna steal a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他們知道你走了嗎  -當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They know you're gone? - Course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出來找馬車  為了一次大搶劫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm out getting a wagon for the big heist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要偷一輛火車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're stealing a train
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛著一個裝滿芥氣的罐車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a tanker car full of yellow cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆  你愿不愿意駕駛一輛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, how would you feel about driving a tanker car
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝滿芥氣的罐車  直接開向華盛頓中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}filled with mustard gas straight into the heart of D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把毒氣灌進這些王八蛋的喉嚨里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And shove it down the throats of these sons of bitches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說芥氣時就吸引到我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had me at mustard gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗恩回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marion's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她帶來了你要的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She brought the people you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的抵抗力量嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is my resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你  我需要六個壯漢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I needed six good people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來偷那輛貨車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to steal that train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我帶來了麥莉和比利·雷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bring me Miley and Billy Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分人都不喜歡你  我盡了最大努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most people don't like you. It's all I could get.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以出入火車場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can get in and out of that train yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比你們能做的多多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is a hell of a lot more than you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎么打架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know how to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者殺人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or kill a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去吧  我想別的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go home. I'll figure something else--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  不行  等等  我們必須幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? No, wait. Look, we got to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須讓我們幫忙  明白吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got to let us help, you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的其他人都支持愛國者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody else in town is waving a patriot flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么這么熱心要加入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why you so hot to join up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁爾斯  這是喬·馬修斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miles, this is Joe Matthews.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他兒子迪倫被愛國者害死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He lost his son Dillon to the patriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去了他們的訓練營\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He went out to their boot camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗恩告訴我  他們搞壞了孩子們的腦袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marion told me how they scrambled those kids' heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們對他做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They did something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再也沒見過迪倫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We never saw Dillon again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們得接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess you'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你在奧斯汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, that's the father
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死的孩子的父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the kid you shot in Austin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要告訴他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等我們搞定這事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not until we get through this mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我會告訴他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, yeah, I'm gonna tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁爾斯  成功不了的  和他們一起不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miles, this is never gonna work, not with these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理  我沒法改變我做過的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie, I can't change the things I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是過去的我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or who I was when I did them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能改變的就是從今以后做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I can change is what I do from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要相信他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're gonna trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的直覺在咆哮  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got every instinct in me screaming no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我盡量想象一個好人的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm trying to picture what a good guy would do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好人會相信他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And a good guy would trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-做個好人真不爽  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Being a good guy sucks. - Yeah, it really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不想回去  -瑪麗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't want to go back. - Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到艾德做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I think about what Ed's done,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what's he's planning to do--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說  天啊  我還打算嫁給他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, my god, I was gonna marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是個好演員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not that good an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會知道不對勁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gonna know something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不回去  他絕對會知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't go back, he'll definitely know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕  吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm scared, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道你很愚蠢  會做正確的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know that you're dumb enough to do the right thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又很聰明  肯定會為此害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and smart enough to be terrified by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到  瑪麗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can do this, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-瑞秋  -亞倫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Rachel? - Aaron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是怎么回事  -我們都沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What the hell is going on? - We're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常  但你得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything is good, but you got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  你沒事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? Really, you're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  拜托  你得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel, please, you got to--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我們家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來了  都看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she's here. She's seen everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不妨告訴她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might as well tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普里西拉是納米機器人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Priscilla's the nano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是它們霸占了她的身體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means that they've taken over her body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把真正的普里西拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they're keeping the real Priscilla
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關在她自己的頭腦里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}locked away inside her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終于能聊一聊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good we can finally speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  面對面的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel, face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和這些人在這里做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing with these people in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月很不可思議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been a weird month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板在動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The floor is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們有一間鼠屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we have a rat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先用老鼠做實驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I started with the rats,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was the same thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多次反復實驗  多次犯錯  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}lots of trial and error, lots of mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在你瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now look at them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自發形成了一個體系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A system in agreement with itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很滿足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are content.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對螢火蟲也做了同樣的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did the same with the fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想這樣對你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to do the same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  但是你們這種物種才瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, but it's your species that's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們的典型特征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's your defining characteristic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對彼此造成傷害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the way you all inflict pain on each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷無情地進食  殺人  達到高潮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this relentless drive to eat, kill, and to orgasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像沒毛的猩猩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like hairless chimpanzees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我好心痛  -你沒有心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It breaks my heart. - You don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have feelings.
