Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  不過他說是關于鍋爐泄露的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, he said something about the boiler having a leak, though.
