Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我們說的做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do what we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你還能回去吃晚飯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you might make it home for dinner.
