Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走  快讓這蠢東西動起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go! Roll this stupid thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁爾斯  有麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miles, problem.
