Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的機會來了  喬  我們走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's your chance, Joe. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, hell.
