Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let 'em get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快點更好  喬  -我在努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Faster would be good, Joe. - I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得說  這挺有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got to admit that was kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴汽笛  喬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull that whistle, Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛剛偷了輛火車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just stole a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.67,0:24:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你不知道似的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.63,0:24:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.31,0:24:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒發現這里面的東西嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you didn't find this in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.94,0:25:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.64,0:25:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.32,0:25:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么緣由嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我很幸福  瑪麗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've made me happy, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.01,0:25:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.66,0:25:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你  艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you too, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.57,0:26:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火車隨時到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Train will be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.67,0:26:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本該帶上所有的堿液\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I'm supposed to take all this lye
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中和芥氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and neutralize the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜一圈  確保沒人跟著我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do a lap. Make sure we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.31,0:26:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟邁爾斯是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what is it with him--Miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.51,0:26:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸看起來像是準備好要殺人一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, my dad looks like he's ready to murder someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.20,0:26:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前欲望更強  自從\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, more than usual, ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.28,0:26:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從邁爾斯把他趕走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since Miles kicked him to the curb?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.95,0:26:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what's the story there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.39,0:26:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不問  不說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't ask, don't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.87,0:26:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真問的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.59,0:26:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子  說真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kid, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.98,0:26:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這么些年來也一直問自己這個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been asking myself that question for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.94,0:26:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論他們之間是怎樣變態的愛恨情仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever twisted love-hate, Cain-Abel brotherhood thing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟之情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they got going,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.90,0:26:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都影響了他們的判斷力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it just clouds their judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.25,0:27:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們都彼此脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes 'em both look weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.77,0:27:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是問題吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a problem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.29,0:27:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要邁爾斯在  我爸就無法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad will never get the republic back
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.65,0:27:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回共和國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as long as miles is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.78,0:27:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean by that?
