Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.22,0:27:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.26,0:27:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出去找更多實驗目標\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's going out to find more test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.41,0:27:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得阻止她  你知道吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to stop her. You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.92,0:27:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的聽覺超好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's got, like, super hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.78,0:27:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們試試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.75,0:27:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉身吧  該死的機器人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turn around, you damn robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.78,0:27:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會阻止你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.87,0:27:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.74,0:27:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.63,0:28:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許它在普里西拉身體里越久  它就會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe the longer it's in Priscilla, it's-- 
