Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  住手  住手  你在找什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, stop, stop. What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.72,0:28:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何有用的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything that might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.59,0:28:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想救普里西拉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to save Priscilla or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.38,0:28:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然想  你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course I do. You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.49,0:28:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.93,0:28:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它控制了我每一個舉動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This thing has been in control of every move I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.56,0:28:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒法反抗  它知道一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't fight it. It knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.15,0:28:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是上帝一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might as well be god.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我為什么會扇她耳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you think I slapped her?
