Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.91,0:31:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓  你們倆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear to god, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.65,0:31:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了你寶貝的邁爾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything for your precious Miles.
