Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.04,0:39:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖襲擊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}against both of our nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.20,0:39:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塞巴斯蒂安·門羅和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}aided and abetted by Sebastian Monroe
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.26,0:39:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁爾斯·麥錫森的幫助下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Miles Matheson.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.81,0:39:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我今天來到這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why I am here today
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.13,0:39:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在卡弗將軍身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to stand beside Genera Carver
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.57,0:39:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式承諾將會提供武器和幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and officially pledge weapons and support
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.52,0:39:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予德州共和國對抗加州恐嚇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the Texas Republic against this California menace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.53,0:39:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  這些加州人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, these Californians--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們站錯了位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're on the wrong side of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.39,0:39:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們試圖撕毀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're trying to rip apart
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.48,0:39:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們變得堅強的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the very thing that makes us strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.95,0:39:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.43,0:40:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.70,0:40:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你沒看到這一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you hadn't seen this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.21,0:40:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.89,0:40:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要殺死所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna kill everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.97,0:40:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.97,0:40:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚說的話是真心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really meant what I said tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.32,0:40:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.60,0:41:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全心全意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.50,0:41:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.09,0:41:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這預示著一個美好的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it signified a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.53,0:41:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無人能熄滅的光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's a light no one can put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.15,0:41:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團結  我們將不會失敗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}United, we will not fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.68,0:41:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要說不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.13,0:41:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用一個詞說出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we say it with one word.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.58,0:41:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.98,0:42:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們全都記住說一句天佑英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}let us all remember to say god bless our heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.03,0:42:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德州共和國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Republic of Texas,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天佑美利堅合眾國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and God bless the United States of America.
